WEBVTT

00:07:59.918 --> 00:08:02.419
And it has a characteristic emphasis.

00:08:02.443 --> 00:08:05.315
(Sings)

00:08:10.924 --> 00:08:13.655
But this characteristic rhythm pattern

00:08:13.679 --> 00:08:15.110
comes from Africa.

00:08:15.580 --> 00:08:18.690
In the ninth century you could find it
in the brothels of Persia,

00:08:18.714 --> 00:08:19.873
and in the thirteenth,

00:08:21.331 --> 00:08:23.993
in Spain, from where,
five centuries later,

00:08:24.017 --> 00:08:26.668
it would cross over to America
with the African slaves.

00:08:27.877 --> 00:08:32.254
Meanwhile, in the Balkans,
it encounters the Roma scale --